        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "A–3 Suppose that each of 20 students has made a choice of anywhere from 0 to 6 courses from a total of 6 courses offered. Prove or disprove: there are 5 students and 2 courses such that all 5 have chosen both courses or all 5 have chosen neither course.",
